  "general_information": "The Gagarin Prospect is a 114,000dwt Aframax tanker built by Hyundai Samho Heavy Industries Co. Ltd. for Sovcomflot. It was designed to run on LNG as a fuel and features WinGD seven-cylinder X62DF engines with low-pressure selective catalytic reduction (SCR) after-treatment systems. The ship has an Ice Class IB (IA Hull) rating and is equipped with advanced safety features, including a gas-fuelled system that meets IMO NOx Tier III limits.",
